    {
      "id": "PopularPost223693",
      "post_content": "Use a cheap creature steal spell like [Act of Treason](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason) or [Mind Control](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Control) to gain control of a creature your opponent controls. Use that creature how you will for the turn, and when you are done with it, sacrifice it before your opponent regains control of it. This is the same concept as the [Fling](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fling) combo, and works just as well depending on your strategy.",
      "posted_by": "MechaKraken",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost223693\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Use a cheap creature steal spell like <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason\">Act of Treason</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Control\">Mind Control</a> to gain control of a creature your opponent controls. Use that creature how you will for the turn, and when you are done with it, sacrifice it before your opponent regains control of it. This is the same concept as the <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fling\">Fling</a> combo, and works just as well depending on your strategy.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy42650\">MechaKraken</span>\r\n                                (1/27/2012 4:32:15 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/Ri